title: MAHADISCOM Jobs 2025 - Apply Online for 136 Apprentice Posts
description: The Maharashtra State Electricity Distribution Company Limited (MAHADISCOM) has officially released the notification to fill the vacancies of 136 Apprentice Posts. Interested and eligibile candidates can use this opportunity to apply for these posts before the last date of application. Candidates who have completed their 10th, ITI can apply for the MAHADISCOM Jobs 2025 . The interested applicants can apply in online mode.
